{"title":"npm基本使用","date":"2020-01-08T09:54:38.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 8, 2020","L":"01/08/2020","MM-DD":"01-08"},"thumbnail":"post/Web/npm基本使用/cover.jpg","link":"post/Web/npm基本使用","categories":["Web"],"updated":"2020-01-08T10:48:10.049Z","content":"<h1 id=\"npm介绍\">npm介绍<a href=\"#npm介绍\" title=\"npm介绍\"></a></h1><p>NPM是NodeJS下的包管理工具，可以解决包依赖问题。</p>\n<h1 id=\"基本命令\">基本命令<a href=\"#基本命令\" title=\"基本命令\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"初始化\">初始化<a href=\"#初始化\" title=\"初始化\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>执行之后当前目录下会生成一个<code>package.json</code>的配置文件。</p>\n<p><strong>package.json配置文件详解</strong></p>\n<ul><li>name 包名</li>\n<li>version 版本号</li>\n<li>description 包描述信息</li>\n<li>main 入口文件，<code>require(&#39;moduleName&#39;)</code>时会加载这个文件，默认为根目录下的<code>index.js</code></li>\n<li>scripts 定义可执行脚本，可使用<code>npm run</code>执行</li>\n<li>author 作者</li>\n<li>license 许可</li>\n<li>devDependencies 开发时所依赖的包，运行时不需要</li>\n<li>dependencies 运行时所依赖的包</li>\n</ul><h2 id=\"安装\">安装<a href=\"#安装\" title=\"安装\"></a></h2><p><strong>全局安装</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install package-name -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>本地安装</strong></p>\n<p>安装包，不修改<code>package.json</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install package-name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>安装包，修改<code>package.json</code>的<code>dependencies</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install package-name --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install package-name -S</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>安装包，修改<code>package.json</code>的<code>devDependencies</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install package-name --save-dev</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install package-name -D</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"卸载\">卸载<a href=\"#卸载\" title=\"卸载\"></a></h2><p><strong>全局卸载</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install package-name -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>本地卸载</strong></p>\n<p>卸载包，不修改<code>package.json</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm uninstall package-name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>卸载包，修改<code>package.json</code>的<code>dependencies</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm uninstall package-name --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm uninstall package-name -S</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>卸载包，修改<code>package.json</code>的<code>devDependencies</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm uninstall package-name --save-dev</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm uninstall package-name -D</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"淘宝镜像\">淘宝镜像<a href=\"#淘宝镜像\" title=\"淘宝镜像\"></a></h1><p>npm默认从国外服务器拉取资源，速度十分缓慢，因此可将其替换成淘宝镜像cnpm.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g cnpm --registry&#x3D;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>使用</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cnpm install package-name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"webpack基本使用","link":"post/Web/webpack基本使用"},"next":{"title":"七大原则","link":"post/设计模式/七大原则"},"plink":"https://beginc.github.io/post/Web/npm基本使用/","toc":[{"id":"npm介绍","title":"npm介绍","index":"1"},{"id":"基本命令","title":"基本命令","index":"2","children":[{"id":"初始化","title":"初始化","index":"2.1"},{"id":"安装","title":"安装","index":"2.2"},{"id":"卸载","title":"卸载","index":"2.3"}]},{"id":"淘宝镜像","title":"淘宝镜像","index":"3"}]}